/* ==========================================================================
  COMMUNITY SHARING SERVICE (.todo)
  Purpose: Share plans, updates, and resources with selected community members
           and collaborate on goals across modules (meals, garden, animals,
           cleaning, projects, calendar).
  Goals:
    1) Clear IA (organized nav + routes)
    2) Intuitive compose → preview → post flow
    3) Consistent design system (btn/card/alert/states)
    4) Event-driven glue (recipes/inventory/calendar/etc.)
    + Empty states, undo, next-best-action after success.

  Aliases assumed:
    "@/components", "@/stores", "@/agents", "@/services", "@/pages", "@/utils"
========================================================================== */

